# breaking changes

0.17.184

- renamed onMount to on:mount
- renamed onUnmount to on:unmount
- renamed pota/web to pota/components
- defaults to attributes instead of properties
- - use `prop:innerHTML` instead of `innerHTML`
- - use `prop:textContent` instead of `textContent`
- - use `prop:value` instead of `value` in `<textarea/>` (textareas dont have an attribute named value)
- - `<textarea value="value here"/>` doesnt work anymore, use `<textarea>value here</textarea>` instead
